<event name="FR_GUARD_WARZONE_PIRATE_DEADCREW">
	<text>You have defeated the Elite Pirate guard. Without crew on board to stop you, you can investigate their cargo. You find a lot of supplies to bring back to the ship, and move on to scrap their hull.</text>
	<autoReward level="HIGH">scrap_only</autoReward>
